        "description": "Severe pain OR heavy blood loss has sent the body into shock — the single low-blood/high-pain crisis. The fighter goes cold, clumsy and blind: strength, dexterity and perception crash, so they barely hit, barely dodge and barely hurt anything.",
        "lethalSeverity": 1.0,
        "floater": true,
